fields.name: frequency, freq
fields.value:
*set how often the video is sent, in minutes*
Usage: b!frequency <minutes>

fields.name: video, url, vid
fields.value:
*set the url of an alternate video to send, or to reset video to default*
Usage: b!video <url>, b!video default

fields.name: channel, chan, sendin, set
fields.value:
*set the channel in which the video should be sent to the current channel*
Usage: b!channel

fields.name: start
fields.value:
*begins the defined message send schedule*
Usage: b!start

fields.name: stop
fields.value:
*stops the current schedule, if any exists*
Usage: b!stop
